        <section id="features">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Automatic check-in for Hoyolab games.</li>
                <li>Supports Honkai Impact 3, Genshin Impact, and Honkai Star Rail.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="installation">
            <h2>Installation</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Clone the repository:
                    <div class="sourceCode">
                        <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/HiraDuong/hoyolab-auto-daily.git</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Navigate to the project directory:
                    <div class="sourceCode">
                        <pre><code>cd hoyolab-auto-daily</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Install the dependencies:
                    <div class="sourceCode">
                        <pre><code>npm install</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Create a <code>.env</code> file and add your configuration settings:
                    <pre class="env"><code>MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_uri
PORT=5000</code></pre>
                    <p>If you donâ€™t know how to get your <code>your_mongodb_uri</code>, see the <a href="#configuration">Configuration</a></p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section id="usage">
            <h2>Usage</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Run the project: <code>npm start</code></li>
                <li>Access the application using your VPS IP or localhost with port 5000. For example:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>For VPS (Virtual Private Server):</strong> <code>&lt;VPS_IP_ADDRESS&gt;:5000</code></li>
                        <li><strong>For Localhost:</strong> <code>localhost:5000</code></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Add an account:
                    <p>Go to <code>localhost:5000</code> you will see this UI</p>
                    <figure>
                        <img src="../usage/home.png" alt="Add Account">
                        <figcaption>Add Account</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
                <li>Add, update or delete a new game:
                    <p>Go to <code>localhost:5000/game</code> you will see this UI</p>
                    <figure>
                        <img src="../usage/listgame.png" alt="List Game">
                        <figcaption>List Game</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    <figure>
                        <img src="../usage/addgame.png" alt="Add Game">
                        <figcaption>Add Game</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
                <li>Update or Delete an account:
                    <p>Go to <code>localhost:5000/account</code> you will see this UI</p>
                    <figure>
                        <img src="../usage/account.png" alt="Account">
                        <figcaption>Account</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section id="configuration">
            <h2>Configuration</h2>
