                <li>Schedule delete the log time:
                    <figure>
                        <img src="../usage/delete_log_schedule.png" alt="Schedule Delete Log">
                        <figcaption>Schedule Delete Log</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
                <li>Get your MongoDB URI here: <a href="https://www.mongodb.com/docs/atlas/getting-started/">Get Started with Atlas - MongoDB Atlas</a></li>
            </ul>
